==English==
===Etymology===
[[Category:Greek derivations]]
From [[Ancient Greek]] '''[[πάνθηρ]]''' (''panther'') "total hunter", from '''[[πάν]]''' (''pan'') "total" + '''[[θήρα]]''' (''thera'') "hunting".

===Proper noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''Panthera'''
#a [[taxonomic]] [[genus]], within [[subfamily]] [[Pantherinae]] - various [[big]] [[cat]]s
